# Search do Obsidian

## Operadores

### AND

O AND é implícito.

Busca:

```text
MERGE INTO iceberg_gold
```

Equivale a:

```text
MERGE
AND INTO
AND iceberg_gold
```

---

### OR

```text
"MERGE INTO" OR "INSERT INTO"
```

---

### NOT

```text
MERGE -INSERT
```

ou

```text
"MERGE INTO" -path:old
```

---

### Frase exata

```text
"MERGE INTO"
```

---

### Busca por pasta

```text
path:saved_queries "MERGE INTO"
```

```text
path:recent_queries FAILED
```

